<h1>Thai massage vs <em>oil massage</em>: which should you get?</h1>
<p class="sub">Two of the most common treatments on every Pattaya massage menu, two completely different experiences. We compare Thai massage and oil (aromatherapy) massage on technique, benefits, what to wear and real prices — so you book the one your body actually needs.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">NS</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Naree Suwan</b>
<span>Naree Suwan · born and raised in Pattaya · wellness &amp; Thai culture writer</span>
</div>
