<h1>30 Best <em>Things to Do</em> in Pattaya</h1>
<p class="sub">Islands, beaches, temples, shows and family days out — a local editor's pick with real prices and how to plan each one.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">DR</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Daniel Reyes</b>
<span>Travel editor · 5 years across Chonburi</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
<span class="when">
<svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16 is-muted"><use href="#pg-clock"></use></svg>
