<h1>Tiffany Show Pattaya: Tickets, Times and Is It Worth It?</h1>
<p class="sub">Pattaya's legendary cabaret, decoded — Tiffany vs Alcazar, seat tiers, show times and whether the spectacle earns its ticket.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">OV</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Olga Vavilova</b>
<span>Senior writer · 7 years living in Pattaya</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
<span class="when">
