<h1>Should you visit Pattaya in the <em>rainy season</em>?</h1>
<p class="sub">The honest answer for anyone weighing a May-to-October trip. We break down what Pattaya is really like in the rain, the real upsides and downsides, and exactly who the green season suits — with current ฿ prices, not brochure ones.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">DR</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Daniel Reyes</b>
<span>Travel editor · 5 years across Chonburi</span>
</div>
