<td><span class="rp r-mid" style="background:#fdecea;color:#b4332b">NO</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="name">01:00<small>Stragglers</small></td>
<td>Most bars closing, kebab vendors busy, drunk crowd peaks, Bolt prices surging</td>
