<h1>Walking Street vs Soi 6 vs <em>LK Metro</em>: which nightlife zone?</h1>
<p class="sub">Pattaya doesn't have one nightlife area — it has three very different ones. We compare Walking Street, Soi 6 and LK Metro on vibe, prices, crowd and timing so you spend your night in the zone that actually fits you.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">OV</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Olga Vavilova</b>
<span>By Olga Vavilova · Senior writer · 7 years living in Pattaya, walking these three sois weekly</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
<span class="when">
<svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16 is-muted"><use href="#pg-clock"></use></svg>
            Updated Jun 10, 2026
          </span>
<div class="share-btns">
<button aria-label="Share this article" type="button"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16"><use href="#pg-share"></use></svg></button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<!-- HERO -->
<figure class="art-hero"><img alt="Pattaya walking street 2 – Walking Street vs Soi 6 vsLK Metro: which nightlife zone?" fetchpriority="high" height="506" loading="eager" src="../Pattaya-Tum-Gorseller-Resized/pattaya-walking-street-2.webp" width="1100"/>
      <figcaption class="cap"><span class="lead"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16"><use href="#pg-pin"></use></svg> Walking Street, Soi 6 &amp; LK Metro · Pattaya's three nightlife zones, compared honestly</span><span class="credit">Go To Pattaya</span></figcaption></figure>
<!-- TL;DR -->
<div class="tldr">
<h4><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-20"><use href="#pg-info"></use></svg> If you only have 30 seconds</h4>
<p><b>Go to Walking Street</b> for the big, loud, once-in-a-trip spectacle — clubs, neon and the most action per metre in Thailand, but the highest drink prices (<b>฿120–250</b>) and the pushiest crowd. <b>Go to LK Metro</b> for the easy middle ground: a compact grid of beer bars and live music with mid-range prices (<b>฿80–150</b>) and a relaxed, social feel. <b>Soi 6 is a daytime/early-evening bar street</b> with a very specific adult character — interesting to walk once, ฿80–120 a drink, but not a general "night out" zone. For most first-timers wanting a proper Pattaya night, <b>LK Metro early then Walking Street late</b> is the move.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- LAYOUT -->
<div class="art-layout">
<article class="art-body">
<!-- MOBILE STICKY TOC -->
<div class="mtoc">
