<h1>Water Sports in Pattaya: Every Option, Price and Safety Tip</h1>
<p class="sub">Parasailing, jet ski, banana boat, flyboard and sea walking — what each costs, where to do it, and how to avoid the classic scams.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">TW</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Tom Whitfield</b>
<span>Activities &amp; adventure editor · Chonburi</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
<span class="when">
<svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16 is-muted"><use href="#pg-clock"></use></svg>
            Updated Jun 10, 2026
          </span>
<div class="share-btns">
<button aria-label="Share this article" type="button"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16"><use href="#pg-share"></use></svg></button>
</div>
